# Copy to .dev.vars to configure `npx wrangler dev` (local development).
#
# LOCAL MODE (POPIA-safe — all AI calls go to Ollama on this machine,
# nothing leaves the machine; Ollama must be running with the model pulled):
LLM_PROVIDER=ollama
OLLAMA_URL=http://127.0.0.1:11434
OLLAMA_MODEL=mistral

# CLOUD MODE (dev against the Anthropic API — fictional data only):
# comment out the three lines above and set:
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Iteration suggestions (both modes): a fine-grained GitHub PAT with contents
# read/write on the repo, used by /api/iteration to commit suggestion files to
# iteration-suggestions/. Without it, iteration analyses fail silently — the
# clinical workflow is unaffected.
# GITHUB_TOKEN=github_pat_...
# GITHUB_REPO=michelle-md/note-prep
# GITHUB_BRANCH=main
